text: Jiang may refer to: *Jiang (surname), several Chinese surnames *Jiang, Common of Kang (Korean name) *Jiang River, an ancient river of China *Jiang (rank), rank held by general officers in the military of China *Jiang County, in Shanxi, China *Chang Jiang, Yangtze River, known as simply Jiang in ancient China *Jiang (restaurant), a restaurant in Guangzhou, China, earning two stars in Michelin Guide for 2020 and one star for 2019 and 2018.
